# Files excluded from `gcloud builds submit` uploads (Cloud Run image build).
#
# By default gcloud falls back to .gitignore patterns when this file is absent,
# which would strip the combined-print-personalized.{en,es}.html templates
# from the Cloud Build tarball — they're gitignored as build artifacts (the
# canonical source is the vendored bowel-prep skill + build_personalized_templates.py),
# but the deployed container DOES need them on disk to serve /render for the
# combined procedure type. This .gcloudignore keeps them in the upload.

.venv/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.env
.DS_Store
*.pdf
# Bundled directions PDFs MUST ship in the container image — they're
# served by app/pdf_assembly.py and merged onto every /render response.
!app/static/directions/*.pdf
/tmp/
.pytest_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.git/
